				<wikidot:authorName>sirpudding</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>348648</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>So there seems to be thing where people confuse early modern English (aka. Shakespearean or Elizabethan English) from the 16th century with Middle English (aka Chaucer's English) from the 11th-15th centuries. This duck doth spake in the former and spaketh not the latter, though he bringeth forth such items as would seems be of the elder age.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
