				<wikidot:authorName>Rigen</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2826105</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The entire thing just feel tacky for me. It's like something piled over one another without clear connection. It's a duck, for some reason. It speaks, in inconsistent vocabulary, for some reason. It trades with old stuff from the 1000s, for some reason. It hates(?) humans, for some reason. It has pocket universe, again, for some unknown reason.</p> 
				 	]]>
