					<![CDATA[
						 <p>In terms of anomalous ducks, <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-2730">SCP-2730</a> and <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-2250">SCP-2250</a> are much more bizarre. As a talking animal, it pales in comparison to <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1845">SCP-1845</a> or <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1867">SCP-1867</a>. And as an eldritch being trapped in the form of a mundane animal, <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-2576">SCP-2576</a> is much funnier.</p> 
				 	]]>
