						 <p>Ducks distributing swords for iPhones is a way to make an SCP, I guess.</p> <p>This is a co-authored work between myself and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaguebearer" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4364963&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1572156392" alt="plaguebearer" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4364963)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/plaguebearer" >plaguebearer</a></span>.</p> <p>Critters include <span class="error-inline"><em>Hot-Coles</em> does not match any existing user name</span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/eskobar" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1173523&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1572156392" alt="Eskobar" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1173523)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/eskobar" >Eskobar</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/janitorcakeworth" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3484414&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1572156392" alt="JanitorCakeworth" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3484414)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/janitorcakeworth" >JanitorCakeworth</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3487700&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1572156392" alt="Uncle Nicolini" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3487700)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/uncle-nicolini" >Uncle Nicolini</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4187885&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1572156392" alt="Rounderhouse" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4187885)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rounderhouse" >Rounderhouse</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alces-alces" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4057128&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1572156392" alt="Alces_alces" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4057128)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/alces-alces" >Alces_alces</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1581620&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1572156392" alt="DarkStuff" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1581620)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/darkstuff" >DarkStuff</a></span>, and <span class="error-inline"><em>HumidHermit</em> does not match any existing user name</span>. Without their help, this article would be very different from where it started. (Super special thanks to Uncle Nicolini for looking this over more times than reasonable. You're a champion.)</p> <p>Image was taken by myself, Rockteeth, after taking a walk in Boise, Idaho and seeing this mallard on the sidewalk. I took the picture, and decided it wasn't worth crossing the duck to go to a gas station for soda, and went back to my friend's house.</p> <p>For more of my works, visit <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/rtme-author">my author page</a>.</p> 
